title: (x) Lifecore Fitness logo, similar to Serpentine - Vibrocentric {Dav}
content: Can't seem to find it... any takers?
author: Chris Washer

comments.content: Yeah. I think it has been stretched a bit. Compared to Serpentine, the crossbar of the 'f' has been cut of, and the leg of the 'R' is square...
Finished with this job. No need to reply.

Anyway, It would have been 'Vibrocentric', by Ray Larabie, _once again_. :)

Dav
